title: Tron Bike Android
description:
Ride you motorcycle snake , avoid crashing into other players tails, tron is one of the classic tron android racing games cut off your opponents before they cut you off!! Note: Increasing the Arena size and adding players reduces performance. Removing players and reducing the arena size improves performance! enjoy tron light cycle bike fast running games and racing games game features.
Options: 
1) Bike Color select from 6 colors. 
2) Toggle Music / SFX on/off .
3) Toggle FPS counter.
4) Change Camera mode. 
5) Select number of players between 2 and 6. 
6) Select Arena Size (Small, Medium, Large).
7) Select Game Speed (Slow, Normal, Fast, Extreme).
